WEBVTT

01:25.720 --> 01:34.990
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.490 --> 01:37.840
[Episode 31]

01:41.310 --> 01:41.810
Why are you suddenly

01:41.810 --> 01:43.300
saying wedding vows?

01:44.229 --> 01:46.210
I've always wanted to marry you.

01:51.430 --> 01:52.160
Just in time.

01:53.780 --> 01:56.850
It's been really tiring lately.

01:57.789 --> 01:59.670
Let's take a day off tomorrow.

02:00.500 --> 02:03.350
I also have something I want to do.

02:04.420 --> 02:05.020
What is it?

02:08.630 --> 02:09.690
Will you go with me?

02:12.150 --> 02:12.750
Okay.

02:34.710 --> 02:37.790
♪ If I have faith in spring ♪

02:39.530 --> 02:42.590
♪ A rainstorm can't bring away
the fragrance of flowers ♪

02:46.680 --> 02:50.230
♪ Those dreams that are hard to realize ♪

02:51.470 --> 02:54.500
♪ Have taken root deep in my heart ♪

02:54.690 --> 02:56.500
How is it? Does it look good?

02:55.060 --> 02:59.340
♪ After countless times of blooming
and withering, I still plant hope ♪

02:57.430 --> 02:58.230
It looks good.

03:00.340 --> 03:01.400
After all the talk,

03:01.920 --> 03:06.040
♪ Seasons change during this trip ♪

03:02.690 --> 03:04.290
this is what you wanted to do?

03:05.210 --> 03:06.910
I was afraid of losing money in business

03:06.890 --> 03:11.420
♪ My eyes become the stars above ♪

03:06.970 --> 03:08.030
and having no money

03:08.080 --> 03:09.810
to buy you a nice wedding dress.

03:10.780 --> 03:12.560
Is it what you imagined?

03:12.010 --> 03:14.070
♪ Time goes by bit by bit ♪

03:13.470 --> 03:14.530
I was worried

03:14.620 --> 03:15.850
that the preparation was too rushed

03:14.730 --> 03:16.500
♪ Leading you and me ♪

03:16.090 --> 03:17.240
and you'd have regrets.

03:17.050 --> 03:20.690
♪ Let days grow into annual rings ♪

03:17.750 --> 03:19.210
It's just what I imagined.

03:20.560 --> 03:21.560
As long as it's you,

03:21.410 --> 03:25.170
♪ Dreams will witness sunset and sunrise ♪

03:22.240 --> 03:23.240
anything is fine.

03:25.930 --> 03:30.600
♪ Amid the sound of footsteps,
I head into the wind of departure ♪

03:31.210 --> 03:33.260
♪ With youth and innocence ♪

03:33.480 --> 03:36.079
♪ With a faint light ♪

03:36.530 --> 03:39.990
♪ Light up a brighter life ♪

03:40.360 --> 03:44.060
♪ Spring lingers on ♪

03:54.400 --> 03:56.280
Sir, I'm sorry.

03:57.240 --> 03:58.500
What's wrong with you?

03:58.500 --> 03:59.620
This is a restaurant,

03:59.620 --> 04:00.750
not a welfare house!

04:01.080 --> 04:02.080
I'm really sorry.

04:02.190 --> 04:03.690
I-I...

04:04.900 --> 04:06.780
I really didn't mean to, Sir.

04:06.800 --> 04:07.860
Can you still work?

04:07.970 --> 04:10.300
How many plates have you broken this week?

04:10.620 --> 04:12.360
Liangliang has had a headache recently.

04:12.360 --> 04:12.960
He's not feeling well.

04:12.960 --> 04:14.060
How many times has he had a headache?

04:14.060 --> 04:14.920
How many times?

04:15.310 --> 04:16.180
If he's really sick,

04:16.180 --> 04:17.839
can he go home and recuperate?

04:19.310 --> 04:21.360
Sir, I'm really sorry.

04:21.390 --> 04:22.220
I'm fine.

04:22.330 --> 04:23.370
I can still hold on.

04:23.370 --> 04:24.230
Please don't.

04:24.370 --> 04:26.060
For the sake of us being compatriots,

04:26.060 --> 04:28.120
I'll still pay you for these two days.

04:29.270 --> 04:30.500
Please find a better job.

04:30.500 --> 04:31.500
Sir, Sir.

04:33.220 --> 04:34.500
Take a break. I'll go talk to him.

04:34.500 --> 04:35.960
He's just angry right now.

04:36.860 --> 04:38.120
Sorry for the trouble.

04:42.420 --> 04:43.680
Have a taste. How is it?

04:46.630 --> 04:48.030
There are plenty of jobs.

04:48.370 --> 04:49.630
If he doesn't want you,

04:50.270 --> 04:51.260
it's his loss.

04:51.690 --> 04:52.420
That's why

04:52.450 --> 04:53.620
we are a couple.

04:54.720 --> 04:56.200
We think alike.

04:57.450 --> 04:58.860
We're good together.

05:07.220 --> 05:08.750
Take advantage of this time

05:10.070 --> 05:11.480
and get a good rest.

05:12.560 --> 05:13.630
Don't work for now.

05:19.890 --> 05:21.010
Aren't you cold?

05:22.100 --> 05:23.290
Don't catch a cold.

05:23.560 --> 05:24.720
It's raining.

05:27.170 --> 05:28.300
I'll hold it for you.

05:34.690 --> 05:35.720
Today,

05:35.900 --> 05:38.030
I don't want to go back so early either.

05:38.680 --> 05:40.460
I want to take you

05:40.510 --> 05:41.659
to a different place.

05:41.659 --> 05:42.520
A wishing well?

05:44.130 --> 05:45.630
This isn't Prague.

05:46.510 --> 05:48.810
I thought we were going to Italy.

05:49.220 --> 05:50.870
Just eat.

05:52.270 --> 05:52.870
Ranran.

05:53.370 --> 05:54.600
It's going to rain.

05:54.680 --> 05:55.570
Let's go back quickly.

05:55.570 --> 05:56.500
I'm not going back.

05:56.500 --> 05:57.810
If it weren't about to rain,

05:57.810 --> 05:58.720
this place would be full of people,

05:58.720 --> 06:00.850
and there wouldn't be any space at all.

06:01.920 --> 06:03.770
There are quite a few people here too.

06:03.770 --> 06:05.120
What's the name of this bridge?

06:05.120 --> 06:07.080
It's called Debilly Footbridge.

06:07.690 --> 06:10.080
That's the Champ de Mars.

06:10.160 --> 06:11.620
That's the Les Invalides.

06:11.740 --> 06:13.070
It was built to connect them.

06:13.070 --> 06:14.470
Constructed in 1900,

06:14.570 --> 06:16.190
it's 99 years old now.

06:17.830 --> 06:18.920
Not bad.

06:20.100 --> 06:22.430
Why are there
so many locks on this bridge?

06:22.930 --> 06:23.700
Look.

06:23.890 --> 06:25.870
There are names on these locks.

06:26.570 --> 06:27.280
They say

06:27.300 --> 06:29.120
-as long as two people in love...
-Really.

06:29.120 --> 06:30.500
...have their names written on it,

06:30.500 --> 06:32.159
they'll be together forever.

06:37.600 --> 06:38.130
I see.

06:38.159 --> 06:39.040
I'll go buy one.

06:40.340 --> 06:41.870
I've already prepared one.

06:43.330 --> 06:44.960
[Liangliang] [Ranran]

06:43.420 --> 06:44.790
You came prepared.

06:45.630 --> 06:46.420
Let's lock it here.

06:46.420 --> 06:47.750
Where should we lock it?

06:47.770 --> 06:48.500
Right there.

06:50.920 --> 06:51.330
Okay.

06:52.210 --> 06:53.270
We'll lock it here.

06:58.700 --> 07:00.280
[Liangliang] [Ranran]

07:05.160 --> 07:06.860
Shen Ranran,

07:07.240 --> 07:10.230
I love you!

07:13.920 --> 07:14.650
Ranran,

07:15.720 --> 07:16.980
no matter where we are,

07:17.040 --> 07:18.570
or whatever form we take...

07:21.420 --> 07:22.750
I will love you forever.

07:25.720 --> 07:26.720
Tao Liangliang,

07:27.070 --> 07:29.100
I love you too!

07:30.500 --> 07:32.150
Shen Ranran,

07:32.210 --> 07:35.020
I love you!

07:35.100 --> 07:36.409
Tao Liangliang,

07:36.560 --> 07:38.370
I love you more!

07:44.560 --> 07:48.330
[Liangliang] [Ranran]

07:53.940 --> 07:54.870
Mr. Chen.

07:55.750 --> 07:56.980
My shop hasn't gone out of business yet,

07:56.980 --> 07:58.980
and you're already here to inspect.

07:59.890 --> 08:00.800
Look at you.

08:01.660 --> 08:03.050
I heard your shop

08:03.500 --> 08:04.360
has run into some trouble.

08:04.360 --> 08:05.130
I came to see

08:05.560 --> 08:06.510
if I could help.

08:07.930 --> 08:09.660
How much inventory is piled up?

08:10.010 --> 08:10.830
Not much.

08:11.070 --> 08:12.870
We're shipping goods every day.

08:12.950 --> 08:14.810
It'll all be gone in a few batches.

08:14.870 --> 08:16.040
How many batches specifically?

08:16.040 --> 08:17.770
Selling 8 or 10 pieces at a time,

08:17.980 --> 08:19.510
you've switched to retail?

08:25.030 --> 08:30.800
[MRX]

08:25.510 --> 08:27.510
I've carefully studied your goods.

08:27.900 --> 08:28.360
Look.

08:29.330 --> 08:30.590
Your goods are not bad.

08:30.890 --> 08:33.570
The fabric, fleece, and zippers

08:33.960 --> 08:35.020
are all top-notch.

08:36.169 --> 08:37.299
The cost is too high.

08:37.789 --> 08:40.250
There are also taxes
and quality inspection procedures,

08:40.250 --> 08:42.179
which are basically just for show.

08:42.669 --> 08:44.650
Putting on the show

08:45.080 --> 08:46.950
has raised your costs by half.

08:47.750 --> 08:48.550
Is it worth it?

08:49.480 --> 08:50.810
On the whole Yabao Road,

08:51.050 --> 08:52.780
no one does business like this.

08:53.770 --> 08:55.270
Using the lowest cost

08:55.600 --> 08:57.000
to get the highest profit

08:57.500 --> 08:58.900
is the way to do business.

08:58.940 --> 09:01.840
You haven't figured out the math.

09:03.620 --> 09:04.360
As for math,

09:05.080 --> 09:06.480
there's short-term math

09:07.250 --> 09:08.430
and long-term math.

09:16.390 --> 09:17.720
I have a small proposal.

09:20.320 --> 09:21.250
Name your price.

09:21.870 --> 09:23.270
I'll acquire your brand.

09:23.840 --> 09:25.030
You can work for me.

09:25.050 --> 09:25.910
What do you say?

09:26.750 --> 09:28.530
Now or never.

09:29.120 --> 09:31.370
A man without money is no man at all.

09:31.840 --> 09:32.640
It's no shame.

09:35.820 --> 09:38.100
I'll think about it.

09:44.340 --> 09:45.270
Hello, Zongbao.

09:45.940 --> 09:46.570
Shengli.

09:47.270 --> 09:49.510
How is your business going?

09:51.480 --> 09:52.040
Not bad.

09:52.150 --> 09:53.250
If I can hold on a bit longer,

09:53.250 --> 09:54.200
it will get better.

09:54.200 --> 09:55.050
It's fine.

09:56.010 --> 09:58.400
I'll help you get through it.

09:59.130 --> 09:59.790
Just now,

09:59.820 --> 10:01.470
I went to the bank in town

10:01.530 --> 10:03.130
and transferred 800,000 to you.

10:03.130 --> 10:03.970
Use it for now,

10:04.370 --> 10:05.630
and see if it's enough.

10:06.770 --> 10:07.650
Zongbao, this is...

10:07.650 --> 10:09.440
Say no more.

10:09.620 --> 10:11.690
Last time I heard you talking,

10:11.720 --> 10:12.960
you were hesitating.

10:13.480 --> 10:14.660
I know.

10:14.890 --> 10:15.860
Whatever it is,

10:15.960 --> 10:18.020
the beginning is always the hardest.

10:18.370 --> 10:19.280
It's okay.

10:19.370 --> 10:21.530
We'll overcome every hurdle together.

10:21.530 --> 10:22.590
I've got your back.

10:23.080 --> 10:24.450
If you need more money,

10:24.600 --> 10:25.390
just tell me.

10:25.840 --> 10:27.970
I have some money coming in next month.

10:29.220 --> 10:30.160
Then, Zongbao,

10:30.500 --> 10:31.960
I won't stand on ceremony.

10:31.980 --> 10:33.130
I will accept the money.

10:33.130 --> 10:34.820
Thank you so much, really.

10:35.360 --> 10:36.920
Don't mention it.

10:37.120 --> 10:38.060
I'm hanging up.

10:38.390 --> 10:39.000
Okay.

10:42.980 --> 10:45.110
When you're out there doing business,

10:45.820 --> 10:48.280
every man has a few good brothers
by his side.

10:50.290 --> 10:51.750
But there's an old saying,

10:52.080 --> 10:54.880
"A good neighbor
is better than a brother far off."

10:54.940 --> 10:56.540
Peers need to stick together

10:56.790 --> 10:57.820
to go further.

10:58.670 --> 10:59.140
Yes.

11:00.460 --> 11:01.750
But good neighbors

11:01.980 --> 11:03.310
should help each other.

11:04.150 --> 11:06.350
You shouldn't take advantage of others

11:06.650 --> 11:08.450
and kick them when they are down.

11:08.500 --> 11:09.960
I heard you have a batch of goods

11:09.960 --> 11:11.110
seized in Russia.

11:11.890 --> 11:12.950
I sincerely

11:12.980 --> 11:14.040
want to remind you.

11:14.870 --> 11:16.030
Grey customs clearance

11:16.030 --> 11:17.500
is a shady business.

11:18.030 --> 11:19.960
You'd better quit while you're ahead.

11:19.960 --> 11:22.290
Having your goods seized
is not a big deal.

11:22.460 --> 11:24.590
If they pursue legal responsibility,

11:25.620 --> 11:27.080
all your years of hard work

11:27.370 --> 11:28.300
would be in vain.

11:30.390 --> 11:31.580
Watch your mouth.

11:32.030 --> 11:34.440
I am a legitimate businessman.

11:38.150 --> 11:38.880
Mr. Chen.

11:39.890 --> 11:41.560
I've always had a feeling

11:41.620 --> 11:42.480
that

11:43.320 --> 11:44.790
you both love and hate

11:44.820 --> 11:47.310
our MRX.

11:47.410 --> 11:48.350
I know a word.

11:48.480 --> 11:50.570
It's called schizophrenia.

11:50.600 --> 11:52.940
It's a disease,
and you should see a doctor.

11:52.940 --> 11:54.120
Then I won't entertain you.

11:54.120 --> 11:55.500
Look around as you please.

11:55.500 --> 11:56.900
I need to do the accounts.

11:57.750 --> 11:58.710
Furthermore,

11:59.410 --> 12:01.410
better a living dog than a dead lion.

12:01.980 --> 12:03.370
You are not qualified

12:03.510 --> 12:05.170
to teach me how to do business.

12:11.500 --> 12:12.250
Master Cao.

12:13.270 --> 12:15.820
Recently, you've worried a lot

12:16.100 --> 12:17.630
about my father's illness.

12:17.860 --> 12:19.010
And you also have to make time

12:19.010 --> 12:20.470
to help me nurse my health.

12:20.700 --> 12:22.150
So I've been looking for an opportunity

12:22.150 --> 12:22.890
to thank you.

12:25.890 --> 12:27.220
It's nothing, Miss Luo.

12:27.890 --> 12:29.820
The chairman is highly respected,

12:31.080 --> 12:32.880
and to be able to do my best for him

12:33.080 --> 12:34.210
is what I ought to do.

12:34.980 --> 12:36.180
To tell you the truth,

12:37.230 --> 12:38.710
there are many people

12:38.740 --> 12:39.870
visiting my father.

12:39.940 --> 12:40.580
But

12:41.100 --> 12:42.620
very few people

12:42.620 --> 12:44.220
can really get the hang of it.

12:45.650 --> 12:47.690
Then I sincerely and eagerly

12:47.720 --> 12:49.180
hope that Miss Luo, you can

12:49.480 --> 12:51.080
point me in the right direction,

12:51.080 --> 12:53.500
so I can

12:53.620 --> 12:55.080
get the hang of it sooner.

12:55.480 --> 12:56.780
I can tell,

12:57.250 --> 12:58.150
Master Cao,

12:58.670 --> 13:00.790
you are different from the others.

13:01.650 --> 13:02.590
You are

13:03.030 --> 13:04.120
not vulgar.

13:04.230 --> 13:05.830
So I'm willing to help you.

13:07.200 --> 13:08.670
My father has been coveting

13:08.670 --> 13:10.350
an item for a long time.

13:10.870 --> 13:13.070
It has recently appeared on the market.

13:13.410 --> 13:14.420
If you are

13:14.440 --> 13:15.570
interested,

13:16.010 --> 13:17.000
I can help you

13:17.100 --> 13:19.560
connect with the seller.

13:24.390 --> 13:25.160
But

13:26.290 --> 13:27.170
the artwork

13:27.200 --> 13:29.510
your father has coveted for so long

13:30.940 --> 13:32.910
must be quite expensive, right?

13:34.360 --> 13:35.170
Don't worry

13:35.170 --> 13:37.070
about the money, Master Cao.

13:37.360 --> 13:38.790
If you don't have enough,

13:39.860 --> 13:41.410
I have some savings.

13:41.670 --> 13:44.750
I can pay for it first.

13:45.030 --> 13:46.360
How could I accept that?

13:46.600 --> 13:47.070
After all,

13:47.070 --> 13:48.790
it's a gift for my father.

13:50.000 --> 13:50.790
Besides,

13:52.030 --> 13:53.590
if we become...

13:55.510 --> 13:56.770
a family in the future,

13:57.360 --> 13:58.960
we won't have to distinguish

13:59.030 --> 14:01.460
between yours and mine.

14:06.800 --> 14:07.600
Rest assured,

14:07.620 --> 14:09.620
I will definitely show the chairman

14:10.630 --> 14:11.290
and you

14:12.120 --> 14:13.750
my determination

14:14.630 --> 14:15.490
and sincerity.

14:25.890 --> 14:26.700
Press the threads firmly for me,

14:26.700 --> 14:27.830
and do it carefully.

14:27.980 --> 14:28.330
Okay.

14:28.440 --> 14:30.090
Cut the ends carefully.

14:30.440 --> 14:30.770
Okay.

14:30.770 --> 14:32.230
Thanks for your hard work.

14:37.220 --> 14:37.710
Hello.

14:37.860 --> 14:39.030
A few distributors

14:39.030 --> 14:40.000
came for inquiries today.

14:40.000 --> 14:42.000
I sent them a few batches of samples.

14:42.240 --> 14:43.670
I think it will work out.

14:43.980 --> 14:45.060
That's great.

14:45.370 --> 14:47.320
We can ship 2,000 more items this week.

14:47.320 --> 14:47.840
That way, we can

14:47.840 --> 14:49.440
take on another small order.

14:49.870 --> 14:50.730
Zhuang Zhuang,

14:50.840 --> 14:52.240
have you noticed

14:52.270 --> 14:53.890
the blizzard in Russia lately?

14:53.890 --> 14:55.030
I heard it's quite severe.

14:55.030 --> 14:56.580
Should we ask Sophia about it?

14:56.580 --> 14:56.910
Yeah,

14:57.120 --> 14:57.910
I was thinking

14:57.910 --> 14:59.150
if we should help out.

14:59.910 --> 15:02.320
Like sending 200 down jackets over?

15:02.690 --> 15:03.570
You're right.

15:04.130 --> 15:04.690
Well,

15:05.100 --> 15:06.430
you contact Sophia,

15:06.460 --> 15:08.080
and I'll arrange the shipment.

15:08.080 --> 15:08.450
Okay.

15:08.480 --> 15:10.380
I'll contact Sophia right now.

15:19.340 --> 15:21.080
Honey, I'm so hungry.

15:21.080 --> 15:22.820
Coming.

15:23.290 --> 15:24.500
Smells delicious.

15:26.410 --> 15:26.740
Here.

15:28.410 --> 15:29.720
Dumplings with wine

15:30.150 --> 15:31.370
make life finer.

15:31.720 --> 15:33.520
Slow down, don't burn yourself.

15:35.790 --> 15:38.920
Here, dumplings for departure
and noodles for arrival.

15:39.460 --> 15:40.140
Honey,

15:40.170 --> 15:42.170
have a safe and pleasant trip

15:42.480 --> 15:44.250
to Lyon.

15:44.440 --> 15:45.500
Come back safely and successfully.

15:45.500 --> 15:46.050
Cheers.

15:46.240 --> 15:46.700
Cheers.

15:54.460 --> 15:55.050
How is it?

15:55.480 --> 15:56.540
Delicious, right?

15:56.940 --> 15:57.600
Delicious.

15:59.750 --> 16:00.620
Let me tell you.

16:02.270 --> 16:03.730
This is what I'm thinking.

16:03.740 --> 16:04.960
Actually, it's a good thing

16:04.960 --> 16:05.940
the travel agency organized

16:05.940 --> 16:07.140
this training for us.

16:07.220 --> 16:07.670
Look,

16:07.770 --> 16:09.510
more and more people from China

16:09.550 --> 16:10.460
are traveling to Europe.

16:10.460 --> 16:11.450
When they come to Europe,

16:11.450 --> 16:12.910
Paris is their top choice.

16:13.200 --> 16:14.770
But the travel industry in Paris

16:14.770 --> 16:16.210
is oversaturated.

16:16.620 --> 16:17.140
You see,

16:17.500 --> 16:20.350
places like Bordeaux, Marseille, and Lyon

16:20.390 --> 16:22.110
also have a lot of great spots.

16:22.870 --> 16:23.570
I was thinking

16:23.570 --> 16:24.310
if I could

16:24.340 --> 16:25.550
develop a new route,

16:25.580 --> 16:26.960
I could earn more money.

16:29.360 --> 16:30.160
In the future,

16:31.650 --> 16:32.460
we can

16:32.510 --> 16:34.230
open our own travel agency.

16:34.750 --> 16:37.720
And further down the road,
we'll go to the South of France

16:37.720 --> 16:38.780
and buy one of those

16:39.050 --> 16:41.630
detached villas with a garden.

16:41.870 --> 16:43.320
We'll plant those

16:43.440 --> 16:46.380
little climbing flowers and plants.

16:47.620 --> 16:49.910
Then we'll get a dog.

16:51.030 --> 16:51.830
A Pomeranian.

16:52.250 --> 16:54.010
And a British Shorthair cat.

16:55.080 --> 16:56.810
And then,

16:56.890 --> 16:58.970
we'll have

16:59.000 --> 17:00.370
a baby.

17:01.370 --> 17:02.370
What do you think?

17:03.980 --> 17:05.040
That's wonderful.

17:05.680 --> 17:07.540
Honey, I didn't expect you to have

17:07.829 --> 17:09.220
so much of the future planned out.

17:09.220 --> 17:10.630
Of course.

17:12.089 --> 17:13.890
Pretty bold thinking, isn't it?

17:15.349 --> 17:16.880
As long as you're by my side,

17:17.440 --> 17:19.770
I'll never have to worry about the future.

17:20.240 --> 17:20.940
Of course.

17:22.250 --> 17:23.940
Here, a toast to you.

17:34.350 --> 17:36.550
Next time, I'll make dumplings for you.

17:37.290 --> 17:39.220
What kind of filling will you make?

17:41.260 --> 17:42.710
Lavender filling.

17:44.400 --> 17:46.530
That filling has quite a strong smell.

17:47.200 --> 17:48.350
What's with that expression?

17:48.350 --> 17:48.850
Let me tell you,

17:48.850 --> 17:49.570
those lavender-scented soaps

17:49.570 --> 17:50.700
made by

17:50.700 --> 17:51.550
French old ladies

17:51.550 --> 17:52.140
sold really well.

17:52.140 --> 17:53.070
I waited for

17:53.090 --> 17:53.900
those Chinese tourists

17:53.900 --> 17:54.810
for 2 hours.

17:54.850 --> 17:56.440
They're soaps after all.

17:56.510 --> 17:58.710
Have you ever seen lavender dumplings?

18:04.420 --> 18:07.000
[Olive Tree Apartment]

18:07.950 --> 18:15.240
[Olive Tree Apartment]

18:10.310 --> 18:11.840
You're just going to study,

18:12.180 --> 18:13.640
but you've packed so much.

18:13.830 --> 18:15.430
Are you planning to leave me?

18:15.570 --> 18:17.100
What are you talking about?

18:17.220 --> 18:18.480
I brought them for my colleagues.

18:18.480 --> 18:19.480
That is more than

18:19.510 --> 18:20.940
what you brought for me.

18:21.200 --> 18:22.530
Are you jealous of that?

18:23.760 --> 18:25.880
[Olive Tree Apartment]

18:31.270 --> 18:32.140
Are you okay?

18:33.330 --> 18:33.960
I'm fine.

18:37.310 --> 18:38.570
Don't pinch your hand.

18:47.180 --> 18:48.590
I'm going to miss you.

18:48.770 --> 18:50.130
I'll miss you too.

18:51.720 --> 18:52.770
While I'm gone,

18:53.710 --> 18:54.830
you must eat on time

18:54.920 --> 18:55.770
and eat more fruits

18:55.770 --> 18:56.920
to get more vitamins

18:57.010 --> 18:58.810
and boost your immunity, got it?

19:00.900 --> 19:02.100
What you just told me

19:02.510 --> 19:04.510
is exactly what I wanted to tell you.

19:05.460 --> 19:06.320
Stay safe.

19:08.070 --> 19:08.770
You're not wearing much.

19:08.770 --> 19:09.700
Hurry upstairs.

19:11.200 --> 19:12.050
Be good.

19:15.000 --> 19:15.770
Then I won't go.

19:15.770 --> 19:16.700
That won't work.

19:17.980 --> 19:19.240
You have to study hard.

19:21.380 --> 19:22.820
Call me if you miss me.

19:28.530 --> 19:29.250
Hurry up.

19:30.200 --> 19:30.980
Stay safe.

20:13.850 --> 20:15.680
These two are so stubborn.

20:15.840 --> 20:18.170
They'll ruin themselves sooner or later.

20:20.420 --> 20:21.820
But they're quite lucky.

20:22.850 --> 20:23.740
They've dodged

20:23.740 --> 20:25.270
the fake down jacket issue.

20:25.270 --> 20:28.200
Mr. Chen, what's your plan?

20:29.460 --> 20:31.190
Let them continue production,

20:31.310 --> 20:33.330
preferably with good quality and quantity.

20:33.330 --> 20:34.000
That way,

20:34.480 --> 20:36.790
I won't have to worry about sales
until next year.

20:36.790 --> 20:38.230
What do you mean?

20:38.570 --> 20:39.400
They

20:39.590 --> 20:40.850
have built their brand

20:41.160 --> 20:42.270
in Russia.

20:42.400 --> 20:43.530
That's a good thing.

20:44.180 --> 20:45.710
The more they stand out now,

20:46.270 --> 20:48.130
the easier it will be for me later.

20:49.210 --> 20:51.470
You want to make high-quality knockoffs

20:51.770 --> 20:52.940
and use their brand

20:53.000 --> 20:54.000
to make a fortune?

20:54.640 --> 20:55.140
Since they

20:55.140 --> 20:56.740
have established the brand,

20:57.640 --> 20:58.390
it has value.

21:00.050 --> 21:01.910
Then it's time for them to get out.

21:17.440 --> 21:18.040
Director,

21:18.750 --> 21:19.740
the first batch of samples

21:19.740 --> 21:20.580
has arrived.

21:21.400 --> 21:23.050
Ship them out as soon as possible
according to this standard.

21:23.050 --> 21:24.180
The more the better.

21:48.350 --> 21:49.250
Hello, hello.

21:49.770 --> 21:50.740
Who are you?

21:51.380 --> 21:52.040
Who are you?

21:52.330 --> 21:53.250
I'm the agent.

21:53.790 --> 21:55.120
Are you looking to rent?

21:58.550 --> 21:59.090
Chairman Luo and his family

21:59.090 --> 22:00.670
were living here fine.

22:01.220 --> 22:02.480
Why is it up for rent?

22:02.500 --> 22:03.460
Where have they gone?

22:03.460 --> 22:04.790
What are you talking about?

22:04.790 --> 22:06.420
The landlord's surname isn't Luo.

22:06.420 --> 22:07.700
The whole family is abroad.

22:07.700 --> 22:09.180
This house has always been listed with me.

22:09.180 --> 22:09.920
No, no.

22:10.700 --> 22:12.510
Chairman Luo
from the investment community?

22:12.510 --> 22:13.510
He has a daughter.

22:13.960 --> 22:14.820
Miss Luo?

22:14.960 --> 22:15.790
And a secretary surnamed Sang.

22:15.790 --> 22:16.820
I come here often.

22:17.240 --> 22:17.740
Are you talking about

22:17.740 --> 22:19.030
the tenant?

22:19.570 --> 22:20.590
Let me tell you,

22:21.000 --> 22:22.640
the whole family is a bunch of scammers,

22:22.640 --> 22:23.570
not good people.

22:23.700 --> 22:25.160
They sold a bunch of

22:25.160 --> 22:26.090
the landlord's mahogany furniture.

22:26.090 --> 22:27.030
I'm assessing the damage right now,

22:27.030 --> 22:28.050
and I'm looking for them too.

22:28.050 --> 22:28.880
Impossible!

22:29.090 --> 22:30.490
Absolutely impossible!

22:31.250 --> 22:32.110
Miss Luo bought

22:32.590 --> 22:33.750
these paintings

22:34.090 --> 22:35.930
and artworks

22:35.960 --> 22:37.440
with real money for her collection.

22:37.440 --> 22:38.480
Alright, alright.

22:38.480 --> 22:39.290
What artworks?

22:39.290 --> 22:40.250
What artworks?

22:40.880 --> 22:42.280
I've had them appraised.

22:42.380 --> 22:43.070
They're all fake,

22:43.070 --> 22:43.930
all forgeries.

22:44.640 --> 22:45.750
Take them if you like.

22:45.750 --> 22:46.550
Nobody cares.

22:47.880 --> 22:49.330
Real money, huh?

22:54.010 --> 22:54.680
Fake?

23:03.610 --> 23:04.390
Impossible.

23:19.620 --> 23:22.780
[Karma catches up. He who deceives
others only deceives himself.]

23:23.050 --> 23:24.120
Scammers!

23:24.290 --> 23:26.580
Cao Ye, this fool, has come to this.

23:27.360 --> 23:29.230
-The money in the trunk...
-He deserves it.

23:29.230 --> 23:31.300
And the fake collection he bought me,

23:31.320 --> 23:33.080
worth over 5 million.

23:33.250 --> 23:35.710
It's probably all his life savings.

23:35.790 --> 23:37.990
You can do whatever you want from now on.

23:38.100 --> 23:38.860
Happy?

23:42.060 --> 23:42.960
Shengli.

23:44.730 --> 23:47.190
I have nightmares
every time I close my eyes.

23:47.770 --> 23:50.120
I thought I could find a bigger sponsor,

23:50.750 --> 23:52.370
get a girl I like,

23:52.860 --> 23:54.320
and make a name for myself.

23:56.160 --> 23:57.690
But I ended up with nothing.

23:58.570 --> 24:01.050
He who deceives others
only deceives himself.

24:01.050 --> 24:02.270
It's karma.

24:08.080 --> 24:09.540
I'm going to report a case.

24:09.830 --> 24:11.360
I'm going to turn myself in.

24:11.510 --> 24:13.910
I can't let those scammers
get away with it.

24:14.230 --> 24:22.880
[Karma catches up. He who deceives
others only deceives himself.]

24:29.070 --> 24:30.600
You are destined to meet me,

24:30.850 --> 24:33.200
and even more destined
to meet my daughter.

24:33.200 --> 24:35.940
You have to learn
to keep your valuables hidden.

24:36.090 --> 24:38.050
Don't show them off all the time.

24:38.840 --> 24:39.900
I've learned a lot.

24:58.210 --> 24:59.900
[Karma catches up. He who deceives
others only deceives himself.]

25:21.220 --> 25:23.010
After that batch of fakes appeared,

25:23.010 --> 25:25.570
even though we've cleared
most of the inventory,

25:25.570 --> 25:27.500
we didn't really make much money.

25:27.980 --> 25:29.110
But recently,

25:29.140 --> 25:30.940
sales haven't been good either.

25:30.960 --> 25:33.160
Is it because the season is almost over?

25:34.500 --> 25:35.760
What are you studying?

25:37.790 --> 25:39.200
Sophia told me

25:39.290 --> 25:40.480
that the Russian market

25:40.480 --> 25:43.010
confiscated several batches
of smuggled goods,

25:43.010 --> 25:44.410
and ours were among them.

25:44.480 --> 25:45.350
Impossible.

25:45.880 --> 25:47.570
We don't have smuggled goods.

25:47.900 --> 25:49.030
I was wondering too,

25:49.110 --> 25:49.920
so I asked her

25:49.960 --> 25:50.720
to bring one out.

25:50.720 --> 25:51.470
Take a look.

25:53.570 --> 25:54.900
Isn't this our stuff?

25:56.980 --> 25:57.680
This is almost

25:57.680 --> 25:59.080
a one-to-one replica.

25:59.660 --> 26:00.170
Look,

26:00.660 --> 26:02.120
even the zipper is a match.

26:09.300 --> 26:09.900
To be honest,

26:09.900 --> 26:11.360
the quality is quite good.

26:11.700 --> 26:12.760
Just look at the workmanship and quality

26:12.760 --> 26:13.830
of that previous batch of fakes—

26:13.830 --> 26:15.420
I can tell right away they're not ours.

26:15.420 --> 26:17.270
But this batch is really different.

26:17.270 --> 26:18.300
For this satin,

26:18.350 --> 26:18.880
I hunted around

26:18.880 --> 26:20.010
several suppliers,

26:20.030 --> 26:20.940
but none of them satisfied me,

26:20.940 --> 26:21.290
and I finally

26:21.290 --> 26:23.490
found it at a large factory in Hangzhou.

26:24.030 --> 26:24.890
And the lining.

26:25.880 --> 26:26.440
I had this color

26:26.440 --> 26:27.930
specially dyed.

26:28.220 --> 26:28.610
I suspect

26:28.610 --> 26:30.090
this is no longer just a knockoff.

26:30.090 --> 26:30.720
They must have found

26:30.720 --> 26:32.640
all our suppliers
and got the goods from them.

26:32.640 --> 26:33.680
If they're capable of

26:33.680 --> 26:34.740
copying our goods,

26:35.290 --> 26:37.020
aren't they just targeting us?

26:39.790 --> 26:41.190
We need to look into this.

26:41.460 --> 26:42.380
If they keep targeting us endlessly

26:42.380 --> 26:42.960
like this,

26:42.960 --> 26:44.040
when will it end?

26:44.770 --> 26:46.230
It has to be investigated.

26:50.200 --> 26:51.460
Hello, Director Yang.

26:52.480 --> 26:54.610
There's something I'd like to ask you.

26:54.920 --> 26:55.630
Yesterday,

26:55.660 --> 26:56.990
we received a knockoff.

26:57.310 --> 26:57.940
It's made almost exactly

26:57.940 --> 26:59.050
like ours.

26:59.680 --> 27:01.210
Even the zipper is the same.

27:01.290 --> 27:02.820
Do you know what's going on?

27:03.460 --> 27:05.420
I've contacted my friend
at the zipper factory.

27:05.420 --> 27:07.050
Because this is custom-made,

27:07.050 --> 27:07.910
I've told him

27:07.940 --> 27:09.640
absolutely not to sell it to anyone else.

27:09.640 --> 27:10.400
But...

27:10.480 --> 27:11.880
this is how the market is.

27:12.220 --> 27:14.160
The better you do,
the more people watch you.

27:14.160 --> 27:15.510
They play little tricks on you.

27:15.510 --> 27:17.840
There's nothing we can do about it, right?

27:19.790 --> 27:20.920
Okay, I understand.

27:20.960 --> 27:21.570
Thanks.

27:33.220 --> 27:35.250
[Honesty is the key to success]

27:37.660 --> 27:38.870
Ms. Zhuang, look.

27:39.980 --> 27:40.900
We've been cooperating

27:40.900 --> 27:41.830
for so long

27:42.230 --> 27:42.920
that I'd never be unwilling

27:42.920 --> 27:44.480
to help you out,

27:44.790 --> 27:45.200
right?

27:45.960 --> 27:47.140
I can't just tell you

27:47.160 --> 27:48.890
who exactly I sold the goods to.

27:49.420 --> 27:51.260
It's not fair

27:51.310 --> 27:52.850
for me to reveal

27:52.880 --> 27:53.940
all our clients' information to you,

27:53.940 --> 27:54.490
right?

27:54.850 --> 27:56.750
Please understand my position.

27:56.900 --> 27:58.300
Here's the situation.

27:59.160 --> 28:00.270
Someone's been knocking off

28:00.270 --> 28:01.330
our stuff.

28:02.180 --> 28:03.010
The workmanship

28:03.010 --> 28:04.250
is exactly the same.

28:05.660 --> 28:07.110
I am gathering evidence now.

28:07.110 --> 28:08.510
If this matter

28:08.830 --> 28:10.430
isn't handled well,

28:10.460 --> 28:11.790
you will be implicated.

28:14.750 --> 28:15.210
Well...

28:19.070 --> 28:20.330
Chen, Chen!

28:20.440 --> 28:20.940
Sir.

28:21.610 --> 28:22.380
Is Mr. Wu here yet?

28:22.380 --> 28:22.840
Yes.

28:23.140 --> 28:24.010
Go entertain him.

28:24.010 --> 28:24.810
I'll be right there.

28:24.810 --> 28:25.230
Alright.

28:25.230 --> 28:26.070
Ms. Zhuang, have a seat.

28:26.070 --> 28:26.810
I've been trying to meet

28:26.810 --> 28:28.870
-with Mr. Wu for a long time.
-Mr. Wei.

28:29.180 --> 28:30.200
For this season's fabrics,

28:30.200 --> 28:31.200
the custom-dyed colors

28:31.200 --> 28:32.140
and texture combinations

28:32.140 --> 28:33.770
are all copyrighted.

28:34.310 --> 28:34.970
Don't think

28:35.000 --> 28:36.290
you can evade responsibility

28:36.290 --> 28:37.290
just because you supplied the fabric,

28:37.290 --> 28:38.720
not the finished garments.

28:38.720 --> 28:39.370
No.

28:39.420 --> 28:40.480
Ms. Zhuang, I—

28:40.500 --> 28:41.220
I am not asking you

28:41.220 --> 28:42.950
to leak customer information.

28:43.050 --> 28:43.980
I am holding you accountable

28:43.980 --> 28:45.460
for leaking ours.

28:48.700 --> 28:49.570
Ms. Zhuang,

28:50.200 --> 28:51.610
we are old friends.

28:52.030 --> 28:53.450
Why must it come to this?

28:53.660 --> 28:54.330
Take a look.

28:54.810 --> 28:55.880
This is a list given to me

28:55.880 --> 28:57.250
by another raw material factory.

28:57.250 --> 28:58.980
See if any names look familiar.

29:10.480 --> 29:11.420
Stack them neatly.

29:11.420 --> 29:12.220
Neatly on top.

29:13.960 --> 29:15.350
Everyone, pitch in.

29:15.380 --> 29:16.180
The boss said

29:16.210 --> 29:18.510
if we finished loading early,

29:18.810 --> 29:20.340
everyone would get a bonus.

29:21.570 --> 29:22.630
Stack them neatly.

29:25.500 --> 29:25.960
Come on.

29:30.350 --> 29:31.550
Neatly on top.

29:31.750 --> 29:33.040
Neatly over there too.

29:33.740 --> 29:35.760
Thanks for your hard work, bro,

29:35.850 --> 29:37.180
in the middle of the night.

29:37.180 --> 29:38.650
I'm a friend of Mr. Chen.

29:39.040 --> 29:40.720
We do business together all the time.

29:40.720 --> 29:42.490
I just happened to pass by,

29:42.640 --> 29:44.220
so I thought I'd check out the goods.

29:44.220 --> 29:45.090
Since you have an appointment
with Mr. Chen,

29:45.090 --> 29:46.490
do you have the order?

29:46.940 --> 29:47.500
The thing is,

29:47.500 --> 29:48.180
we had dinner a few days ago,

29:48.180 --> 29:48.500
and he said

29:48.500 --> 29:49.920
there'd be a good batch of goods tonight.

29:49.920 --> 29:51.250
If these goods reach Yabao Road,

29:51.250 --> 29:52.790
there won't be any left for me.

29:52.790 --> 29:53.770
I want to take a look first,

29:53.770 --> 29:54.880
so I know what to expect.

29:54.880 --> 29:56.110
That way, when I talk to Chen,

29:56.110 --> 29:57.040
it'll be easier.

29:57.570 --> 29:58.370
What's going on?

29:58.370 --> 29:59.180
Well...

29:59.350 --> 30:00.350
Bro, do you smoke?

30:00.510 --> 30:01.760
Here, have a pack.

30:02.380 --> 30:03.790
Take it, come on.

30:06.090 --> 30:06.860
Let him see.

30:06.970 --> 30:08.090
Okay, thanks, thanks.

30:08.090 --> 30:08.680
You can look,

30:08.680 --> 30:09.790
but don't get them dirty or ruin them.

30:09.790 --> 30:11.420
-Rest assured.
-Or we won't be able to explain it.

30:11.420 --> 30:13.020
Rest assured, rest assured.

30:34.440 --> 30:38.170
I thought it was a competitor spying on us
in the middle of the night.

30:40.790 --> 30:42.450
You can't sell your own goods,

30:43.830 --> 30:45.160
so you sneak around copying me?

30:45.160 --> 30:45.630
Chen Guangfa,

30:45.630 --> 30:46.830
you're interesting.

30:47.500 --> 30:48.870
Who's copying who here?

30:49.480 --> 30:50.530
You tell me.

30:51.610 --> 30:53.140
This is called plagiarism.

30:53.220 --> 30:54.330
It's illegal.

30:54.360 --> 30:56.290
Which eye did you see me
plagiarizing with?

30:56.290 --> 30:56.740
Isn't this

30:56.740 --> 30:58.070
exactly the same thing?

30:58.830 --> 31:00.270
Don't think I don't know

31:00.500 --> 31:02.030
once these goods go abroad,

31:02.220 --> 31:03.880
you'll put your label on them.

31:04.900 --> 31:06.200
You think I can't find out?

31:06.200 --> 31:06.850
There are plenty of down jackets

31:06.850 --> 31:08.620
processed in my factory.

31:09.070 --> 31:10.750
Which batch are you talking about?

31:10.750 --> 31:13.090
If you want trouble,
go find the ones who ordered it.

31:13.090 --> 31:14.810
Or show me the evidence.

31:17.830 --> 31:18.630
Chen Guangfa.

31:20.570 --> 31:21.870
Previously in Russia,

31:22.660 --> 31:24.190
it was you who used our brand

31:24.420 --> 31:26.080
to make counterfeits, right?

31:26.530 --> 31:27.570
Do you think I'm the only one

31:27.570 --> 31:28.510
you've hurt?

31:29.240 --> 31:30.000
You've tarnished

31:30.000 --> 31:32.660
the reputation
of all Chinese businesspeople.

31:32.750 --> 31:33.480
Don't you just want

31:33.480 --> 31:34.610
to acquire my brand?

31:34.640 --> 31:35.570
I am telling you,

31:35.940 --> 31:37.600
it is absolutely impossible.

31:38.320 --> 31:39.780
After a bunch of nonsense,

31:40.180 --> 31:41.980
you've finally got to the point.

31:42.790 --> 31:43.920
Since you are here,

31:44.400 --> 31:46.000
I will point out a way for you.

31:46.270 --> 31:47.740
Since your goods can't be shipped,

31:47.740 --> 31:49.680
you are losing money every day, right?

31:49.680 --> 31:50.340
Think about

31:51.240 --> 31:53.370
those workers who can't afford to eat.

31:54.010 --> 31:54.830
Xu Shengli.

31:56.770 --> 31:57.500
Shengli.

31:58.250 --> 32:00.570
How can they succeed by following you?

32:04.200 --> 32:05.190
Think about it.

32:05.220 --> 32:07.660
I will acquire you at a discounted price.

32:07.720 --> 32:08.720
What do you think?

32:19.180 --> 32:19.890
Come often.

32:22.350 --> 32:23.510
With Chen Guangfa doing this,

32:23.510 --> 32:24.440
can't we sue him?

32:26.860 --> 32:27.550
We currently

32:27.550 --> 32:29.090
have too little evidence.

32:29.190 --> 32:30.460
Suing him now

32:30.540 --> 32:31.740
would just alert him.

32:32.000 --> 32:32.720
But it is fine.

32:32.720 --> 32:33.920
I've talked to Sophia

32:34.350 --> 32:35.720
and asked her to help us collect

32:35.720 --> 32:38.310
evidence of him using our trademark
in Russia.

32:38.310 --> 32:39.510
The top priority now

32:39.810 --> 32:41.000
is to take back the market

32:41.000 --> 32:42.000
that he occupied.

32:42.140 --> 32:42.530
Otherwise,

32:42.530 --> 32:43.920
if we fight this international lawsuit,

32:43.920 --> 32:45.580
this season will be long over.

32:45.610 --> 32:46.570
The things he makes

32:46.570 --> 32:48.030
are about the same as ours.

32:48.400 --> 32:50.660
Although the down content isn't as high,

32:50.680 --> 32:52.050
it still isn't cheap.

32:53.220 --> 32:54.680
How can the price be so low?

32:54.810 --> 32:56.740
It must be grey customs clearance.

32:57.000 --> 32:58.110
With chartered transport
and taxes included,

32:58.110 --> 32:59.740
the cost price is much lower.

33:01.770 --> 33:04.070
The brand we've worked hard to build

33:04.270 --> 33:06.000
ended up paving the way for him.

33:09.000 --> 33:10.920
Oh, right, look at this.

33:12.800 --> 33:13.990
[Hebei Shengda Garment Trading Firm]
[Wang Yuhua]

33:13.400 --> 33:14.400
I've visited almost

33:14.400 --> 33:15.240
all the raw material suppliers

33:15.240 --> 33:16.140
in person.

33:16.190 --> 33:18.730
[Hebei Shengda Garment Trading Firm]
[Wang Yuhua]

33:16.460 --> 33:17.360
This company

33:17.480 --> 33:19.050
appears on several suppliers'

33:19.050 --> 33:19.980
purchase lists.

33:20.240 --> 33:21.410
One or two is fine,

33:22.070 --> 33:22.610
but to know

33:22.610 --> 33:24.470
so much specific information...

33:27.150 --> 33:27.730
Meng.

33:33.960 --> 33:34.980
Still giving orders?

33:34.980 --> 33:35.500
Yes.

33:35.590 --> 33:37.520
The bigger the orders, the better.

33:37.660 --> 33:39.020
Mr. Chen, didn't you say before

33:39.020 --> 33:39.850
that after bankrupting them,

33:39.850 --> 33:41.400
you would give the shop to me?

33:41.400 --> 33:42.720
It's been several months.

33:42.720 --> 33:44.780
Why are you still giving them orders?

33:44.920 --> 33:45.580
Didn't they

33:45.590 --> 33:47.190
borrow a lot of money before?

33:47.670 --> 33:49.450
We can't let them borrow it for nothing.

33:49.450 --> 33:51.250
We have to make them spend it all.

33:51.700 --> 33:52.750
Keep this in mind:

33:53.010 --> 33:54.810
The size of their new order

33:55.790 --> 33:56.790
determines how much

33:56.790 --> 33:58.070
they end up overspending.

33:58.070 --> 33:59.800
I want to take them down at once.

34:00.250 --> 34:01.980
I can't let them stand up again.

34:04.010 --> 34:05.120
[Down Jacket]

34:05.120 --> 34:08.120
[Beijing MRX Trading Co., Ltd.]

34:08.219 --> 34:09.570
[The Seller]
[Beijing MRX Trading Co., Ltd.]

34:09.590 --> 34:10.510
[Quantity: 20,000]

34:11.460 --> 34:12.760
Am I seeing this right?

34:13.120 --> 34:14.159
Such a big order!

34:14.380 --> 34:15.300
Are we really gonna take it?

34:15.300 --> 34:17.340
Yes, we have to!

34:18.570 --> 34:19.030
Well...

34:19.730 --> 34:21.030
That's 20,000 pieces.

34:21.980 --> 34:22.860
If this order goes through,

34:22.860 --> 34:24.170
our cash flow will be fine, right?

34:24.170 --> 34:24.440
Yes.

34:25.460 --> 34:26.040
Yeah.

34:26.420 --> 34:27.380
It looks like

34:27.400 --> 34:29.330
things are really getting better.

34:29.530 --> 34:30.530
Shengli, Zhuang.

34:30.590 --> 34:32.190
I've read the contract.

34:32.900 --> 34:34.030
It's just this clause.

34:34.030 --> 34:35.440
The deposit they're putting down

34:35.440 --> 34:36.380
is a bit low.

34:36.920 --> 34:38.230
Can we negotiate it?

34:39.500 --> 34:41.360
That's pretty hard to negotiate.

34:41.880 --> 34:43.860
We already talked about it
for a long time.

34:43.860 --> 34:44.840
True.

34:45.150 --> 34:46.460
But I've checked the contract.

34:46.460 --> 34:47.670
Except for this clause,

34:47.670 --> 34:48.600
the rest is fine.

34:48.760 --> 34:49.960
Then don't hesitate.

34:50.460 --> 34:52.360
Notify the factory and start!

34:52.780 --> 34:53.170
Okay.

34:54.530 --> 34:56.630
But with such a large batch of goods,

34:56.940 --> 34:57.920
do we have enough funds?

34:57.920 --> 34:59.460
Honey, how much money do we have left?

34:59.460 --> 35:00.460
Around 2 million.

35:00.860 --> 35:02.000
Then I'll find a way

35:02.050 --> 35:03.550
to borrow another million.

35:03.550 --> 35:06.050
If we're shipping,
let's ship the full amount.

35:06.050 --> 35:07.330
Three million.

35:07.500 --> 35:09.280
Shengli, are you sure?

35:10.320 --> 35:13.100
If we do it, let's do a big one.

35:13.400 --> 35:15.350
Nail them down with one blow!

35:15.510 --> 35:16.170
Let's do it.

35:21.280 --> 35:23.480
Make sure all the buttons are attached.

35:23.490 --> 35:23.920
Okay.

35:34.190 --> 35:35.280
Good job.

35:40.890 --> 35:41.550
How is it?

35:43.460 --> 35:44.360
Nobody came at all,

35:44.360 --> 35:46.020
and no one answered the phone.

35:46.230 --> 35:47.690
Is there something wrong?

35:49.900 --> 35:51.660
They probably bailed on the order.

35:51.660 --> 35:52.720
-Bailed?
-Bailed?

35:53.410 --> 35:54.470
Such a big order...

35:54.900 --> 35:55.360
But

35:55.530 --> 35:57.080
didn't they already pay the deposit?

35:57.080 --> 35:59.140
We don't have time to argue with them.

35:59.460 --> 36:00.360
In another month,

36:00.360 --> 36:01.890
the coldest time will pass.

36:02.090 --> 36:03.030
I'll ask right now

36:03.030 --> 36:06.050
if we should ship the goods back
without clearing customs first.

36:06.050 --> 36:06.910
For this batch,

36:07.460 --> 36:09.010
let's get in touch
with our regular distributors

36:09.010 --> 36:10.740
and see if they can help sell it.

36:10.960 --> 36:13.070
It's fine.
Continue with customs clearance.

36:13.070 --> 36:15.070
If worst comes to worst, we'll lower

36:15.260 --> 36:16.390
the price a bit more.

36:17.230 --> 36:18.280
Okay, I'll contact them immediately.

36:18.280 --> 36:18.810
Go ahead.

36:24.900 --> 36:25.400
Mr. Xu.

36:27.070 --> 36:28.070
Need any help?

36:29.050 --> 36:30.650
Tell me if you need anything.

36:31.480 --> 36:32.650
We are neighbors.

36:44.590 --> 36:45.190
Exciting.

36:45.800 --> 36:47.510
He wanted to take me out with one blow,

36:47.510 --> 36:48.710
but little did he know

36:48.890 --> 36:50.290
this is a pendulum.

36:53.260 --> 36:53.910
Mr. Chen,

36:54.280 --> 36:55.000
they are very determined this time,

36:55.000 --> 36:56.340
putting all their money

36:56.480 --> 36:57.580
on the line.

36:57.610 --> 36:58.890
I'll make exactly

36:58.910 --> 36:59.970
as many as they do,

37:00.250 --> 37:02.050
and they'll be exactly the same.

37:02.440 --> 37:04.240
When their goods reach customs,

37:04.280 --> 37:06.120
you declare them

37:06.260 --> 37:08.010
under the name of Guangfa Commerce.

37:08.010 --> 37:09.230
Then make a fake customs declaration form

37:09.230 --> 37:10.670
for their MRX.

37:10.700 --> 37:12.160
Then my fake goods

37:12.190 --> 37:13.450
will become real ones.

37:13.550 --> 37:15.210
Using the brand they created,

37:15.230 --> 37:16.280
we will make a fortune

37:16.280 --> 37:18.300
this winter.

37:21.060 --> 37:22.890
Without real documents,

37:23.030 --> 37:24.610
their goods will be detained at customs.

37:24.610 --> 37:25.660
It won't be long

37:25.850 --> 37:27.210
before their capital chain snaps

37:27.210 --> 37:28.470
and they're finished.

37:28.820 --> 37:29.980
When the heat is off,

37:30.090 --> 37:32.650
I'll find someone to get the goods out.

37:34.710 --> 37:36.680
You can do that?

37:37.460 --> 37:39.510
As long as the goods
are detained at customs,

37:39.510 --> 37:40.970
there will be no evidence.

37:42.210 --> 37:42.840
Mr. Chen,

37:43.420 --> 37:44.550
but their goods

37:44.550 --> 37:45.500
are worth 3 million.

37:45.500 --> 37:47.030
Didn't you have a batch of goods

37:47.030 --> 37:47.860
seized before?

37:47.860 --> 37:48.300
Do you still have

37:48.300 --> 37:49.560
that much cash on hand?

37:51.390 --> 37:53.370
Even if I go bankrupt this time,

37:53.930 --> 37:55.150
I will take them down.

37:56.630 --> 37:57.390
By then,

37:57.550 --> 37:58.920
not only will the proceeds
from these two shipments

37:58.920 --> 37:59.620
be mine,

38:01.590 --> 38:03.450
but their brand will also be mine.

38:08.440 --> 38:10.240
I won't forget my promise to you.

38:13.880 --> 38:14.690
Mr. Chen,

38:15.730 --> 38:17.160
it sounds to me like

38:17.380 --> 38:19.500
you want to turn the whole of Yabao Road

38:19.500 --> 38:21.480
into Guangfa Commerce.

38:23.360 --> 38:24.320
I am filtering out

38:24.320 --> 38:25.580
people I can work with.

38:26.760 --> 38:27.960
This young couple...

38:30.690 --> 38:32.350
has disappointed me too much.

38:32.900 --> 38:34.760
They don't respect market rules.

38:37.170 --> 38:38.900
They need to be taught a lesson.

38:42.500 --> 38:44.120
Mr. Chen, I'm leaving now.

38:51.620 --> 38:53.340
Take care, Mr. Meng.

39:15.300 --> 39:16.400
Liangliang!

39:17.260 --> 39:18.360
Tao Liangliang!

39:19.190 --> 39:20.100
Liangliang!

39:23.880 --> 39:24.630
Where is he?

39:47.100 --> 39:48.870
My dear baby Ranran,

39:49.710 --> 39:52.770
please forgive me
for leaving without saying goodbye.

39:53.070 --> 39:54.870
I've actually been thinking it

39:55.210 --> 39:56.830
for a long time.

39:57.090 --> 39:58.790
Even though I have

39:59.340 --> 40:01.190
so much reluctance in my heart,

40:02.460 --> 40:03.830
I still decided

40:04.980 --> 40:05.670
to leave.

40:08.980 --> 40:09.600
Ranran,

40:10.300 --> 40:13.980
something is wrong with my body.

40:16.510 --> 40:20.320
I believe if you knew,

40:21.880 --> 40:24.340
you would definitely
take me to get treated.

40:25.260 --> 40:26.920
I've asked around carefully.

40:28.000 --> 40:29.530
It can't be cured

40:30.710 --> 40:32.370
either in France or back home.

40:32.940 --> 40:35.400
It really isn't worth it

40:36.570 --> 40:38.570
to spend all the money on treatment.

40:39.800 --> 40:42.780
I'm only willing
to leave this hard-earned money

40:43.840 --> 40:45.360
to you and your parents.

40:44.870 --> 40:47.370
[Shen Ranran]

40:47.610 --> 40:48.800
You still have a future.

40:48.800 --> 40:50.330
You need to live your lives.

40:52.100 --> 40:54.310
[Shen Ranran]

40:52.260 --> 40:53.140
Ranran,

40:54.180 --> 40:57.550
I remember every wonderful moment—

40:54.330 --> 40:57.720
[Tao Liangliang]

40:58.440 --> 41:01.170
from the day we met,
to getting to know each other,

41:02.000 --> 41:04.960
and finally holding each other
in our arms.

41:08.260 --> 41:09.790
Every time I think about it,

41:10.400 --> 41:11.860
I feel

41:12.480 --> 41:16.520
so happy and warm.

41:18.470 --> 41:22.590
But this happiness is too short.

41:25.030 --> 41:26.260
But I'm content.

41:29.900 --> 41:30.510
Ranran,

41:32.110 --> 41:33.640
even though I can barely see

41:34.170 --> 41:35.600
right now,

41:34.570 --> 41:36.500
[Name: Tao Liangliang]

41:38.090 --> 41:41.860
I still don't want to see you

41:42.200 --> 41:44.660
[Name: Tao Liangliang]

41:43.110 --> 41:43.860
cry over

41:43.860 --> 41:48.480
our upcoming goodbye.

41:53.170 --> 41:54.670
Please

41:55.610 --> 41:57.810
listen to me for the last time.

42:00.010 --> 42:01.020
Don't come to me.

42:03.150 --> 42:06.800
Let me leave quietly.

42:16.110 --> 42:17.780
Without me,

42:19.470 --> 42:23.560
you have to be strong.

42:25.650 --> 42:27.210
I'll be far away,

42:27.760 --> 42:30.940
[Name: Tao Liangliang]

42:28.030 --> 42:31.550
watching you quietly,
staying by your side.
